data.description: SW Cape Coral corner lot with assessments in and paid under 300k! Just waiting for its new forever owners. This home is situated on a corner lot with a nice-sized fenced-in backyard. Three bedroom two bath, two car garage, with ample sized indoor laundry room. Beautiful statement granite stone in the kitchen, stainless steel appliances. The home did sustain roof damage during Hurricane Ian, tarped roof, and no interior damage. Convenient location minutes to schools, shopping, and entertainment.
